{"tid":2412114,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國外交部把香港改稱區域樞紐　未再直接描述香港享有高度自治","createTime":"2021-02-17T23:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T03:47:05.000Z","uid":230530,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02a9c1faeb4e2c1771feeee1a34414572693c729","tid":2412114,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:50:38.000Z","msg":"英國外交部更新在香港營商指引，把香港的經濟概述由「國際金融中心」描述改為「區域樞紐」，在反洗黑錢中，指香港作為國際金融中心，仍然是不合法及合法金融的目標。更新的指引中，未再直接描述香港享有高度自治，改為指香港在一國兩制模式下運作，《中英聯合聲明》規定香港除外交及防務外，在經濟及貿易其他領域上享有高度自治。<br />\n<br />\n指引又提及《港區國安法》在港實施，引述英國的香港半年報告，批評國安法削弱港人基本權利和自由，違反《中英聯合聲明》，指引又指香港的言論自由令人關注，有表面證據顯示有公司因為員工的政見，包括參與抗議活動，受到中國當局的壓力。"},{"pid":"9538cfd0286e35a35e870b2be194fab967e10b7f","tid":2412114,"uid":54940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e293583b18bc934b15e0f271cc5310374b9a6b","tid":2412114,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T23:58:15.000Z","msg":"强烈不滿 堅決反對"},{"pid":"744f4a44d4d1ade7c7b0a55ef7f015abc6df5510","tid":2412114,"uid":277992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:00:46.000Z","msg":"國際金融中心地位係基本法腐乳"},{"pid":"0f5ad3efc659257c84f4117ab6c93e6e1ecb9ce3","tid":2412114,"uid":221171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:17:57.000Z","msg":"明明已經有國安法 同 無晒反對黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解香港變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44fe630d98d166876a7a509653fb60c14a535f4","tid":2412114,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"744f4a44d4d1ade7c7b0a55ef7f015abc6df5510","tid":2412114,"uid":277992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:00:46.000Z","msg":"國際金融中心地位係基本法腐乳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T00:23:09.000Z","msg":"本身港共個香港定位係亞洲國際都會，所以區域輸扭個定位係啱既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a500b07ad631eab381857d07185f8346e1325542","tid":2412114,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"冇左好內"},{"pid":"2b2d2169ab04e7e35dc5a20c7523e92aa1910217","tid":2412114,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T03:45:40.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2da96bc2502194dbdd815dcca5caf794ccd04c","tid":2412114,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24gcMDE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24gcMDE.gif&h=adaf551c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}